{"priority": "major", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1910/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1910.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1910/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1910/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1910/flaky-race-condition-in-unit_visual_test"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1910/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "title": "Flaky race condition in UNIT_Visual_TEST during SetTransparency", "component": {"name": "rendering", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/components/122881.json"}}}, "votes": 0, "watches": 1, "content": {"raw": "I observed a seg-fault of `UNIT_Visual_TEST` during the `DerivedTransparency` test ([full details here](https://gist.github.com/scpeters/033c6c99b7ad0526a185707ac61b49d7)).\r\n\r\nThe main thread was calling `Visual::SetTransparency` ([Visual_TEST.cc:573](#!/osrf/gazebo/src/a0e43939bd97680b/gazebo/rendering/Visual_TEST.cc#Visual_TEST.cc-573))\r\nwhile the sensor thread was calling `ImageSensorContainer::Update`, `Scene::PreRender`, ... `Visual::GetShaderType`. These simultaneous calls lead to a seg-fault.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I observed a seg-fault of <code>UNIT_Visual_TEST</code> during the <code>DerivedTransparency</code> test (<a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://gist.github.com/scpeters/033c6c99b7ad0526a185707ac61b49d7\" rel=\"nofollow\">full details here</a>).</p>\n<p>The main thread was calling <code>Visual::SetTransparency</code> (<a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/src/a0e43939bd97680b/gazebo/rendering/Visual_TEST.cc#Visual_TEST.cc-573\" rel=\"nofollow\">Visual_TEST.cc:573</a>)\nwhile the sensor thread was calling <code>ImageSensorContainer::Update</code>, <code>Scene::PreRender</code>, ... <code>Visual::GetShaderType</code>. These simultaneous calls lead to a seg-fault.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2016-03-30T20:36:41.880668+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:22:47.202168+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1910}